column4: A: switch to insert mode after current line
column5: d: list directories to jump to

column4: o/O: open line below/above current and switch insert mode

column5: C+r: search for entry in command history

column4: ^: Move to first non blank character of line
column5: Alt+c: set sub directory as working directory

column3: Pre+Tab: Choose copy in command history

column1: O: Open URL in new tab
column3: Pre+/ Copycat Search in command output

column1: gf: cycle focus to next frame
column4: C+W n: Split horizontally and edit a new file
C+W ^: Split with alternate file (# buffer)
C+o/i: Go to previous/next cursor positions
g Comma /g; : Jump to previous/next change in change list
C+x C+p autofill word from document
C+x C+l autofill line from document
